    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@value": "Exercises that train the trunk to resist rotational forces — the spine is braced against a load that attempts to rotate it. Representative: Pallof press, single-arm carry, single-arm cable row."
