      {
        "@value": "A fundamental category of human movement that describes the mechanical structure of an exercise. Exercises sharing a movement pattern make similar demands on the musculoskeletal system and may serve as substitutes for one another."
      }
    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#label": [
