    ],
    "http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#comment": [
      {
        "@value": "Exercises that train the trunk to resist flexion forces — the spine is braced against a load that attempts to flex it. Representative: back extension, Superman hold, good morning with isometric hold."
